  "description": "A Simple ScoreHud Addon that allows you to use {credits} in the config with the Credits by LaithDev",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-creditsscore\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#creditsscore\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>CreditsScore</h1>\n<p>A Simple ScoreHud Addon that allows you to use {credits} in the config with the Credits by LaithDev</p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-how-does-it-work\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#how-does-it-work\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>How does it work?</h1>\n<p>Its very simple, go into your scorehud plugin_data folder and find ScoreHud.yml, then go to the line which holds the configurable scoreboard then add {credits}, example:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-yaml\"><pre>- <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>Credits: {player.credits}<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span></pre></div>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-what-if-i-catch-an-issue\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#what-if-i-catch-an-issue\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>What if i catch an issue?</h1>\n<p>Report the issue in github by the issues tab\nu can do that by clicking this link: <a href=\"https://github.com/ItsToxicGG/CreditsScore/issues\">https://github.com/ItsToxicGG/CreditsScore/issues</a></p>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
